sources.title: Confidential
sources.description: It's G-men versus the numbers racket in this fast-moving second feature crime drama with an unusually large cast headed by Donald Cook and Evalyn Knapp. Directed by Edward L Cahn. Released in 1935 Complete print

metadata.Plot: A federal agent goes undercover to avenge the murder of a friend but one of the gang thinks he seems familiar.
metadata.Writer: John Rathmell, Scott Darling, Wellyn Totman
metadata.Actors: Donald Cook, Evalyn Knapp, Warren Hymer
